ity also lasts a longer time than\nunbounded case, which shows the initial quantum state of the atom is protected\nby the boundary for two cases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Jul 2020 09:11:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-28"}
