 presents current problems\nof this technique. In contrast to that, the unusual approach of capacitive\nsensing demonstrates a high potential regarding vital signs acquisition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Jul 2020 11:25:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-28"}
