y the entraining air are shown to mechanistically\ndetermine specific physical modes of transmission and variation in the basic\nreproduction number $\\mathcal{R}_0$, from first principle calculations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Jul 2020 14:28:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 1 Aug 2020 01:45:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 1 Sep 2020 15:24:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-08"}
