n of the sample size calculators. This proposed\ndesign is motivated by our involvement in the Diabetes and Mental Health\nAdaptive Notification Tracking and Evaluation (DIAMANTE) study. This study uses\na novel mobile application, also called \"DIAMANTE\", which delivers adaptive\ntext messages to encourage physical activity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Jul 2020 14:53:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-29"}
